headline.main: PROPAGANDA AND ROCKETS SOAR IN SPACE AGE

results.snippet: THE chief political impact of the space age to date has been in the area of propaganda influencing the minds of men. The chief beneficiary of this impact has been, and is, the Soviet Union. That country's world prestige has been shot upward by the...
results.lead_paragraph: THE chief political impact of the space age to date has been in the area of propaganda influencing the minds of men. The chief beneficiary of this impact has been, and is, the Soviet Union. That country's world prestige has been shot upward by the same rockets which have put its sputniks, luniks, and manned space vehicles into flight.

headline.main: America's Sleeping Sickness -- Staying Awake; With sleeplessness rife in the land, it might be said that the American Dream today is to sleep. What is sleep, and can insomnia be cured? Sleeping Sickness

results.snippet: AMONG the minor marvels of cosmonaut Gherman S. Titov's constitution, certainly one of the more uncanny is the ease with which he can drop off to sleep, even while circling the earth every eighty-eight minutes. When last in orbit, Major Titov says...
results.lead_paragraph: AMONG the minor marvels of cosmonaut Gherman S. Titov's constitution, certainly one of the more uncanny is the ease with which he can drop off to sleep, even while circling the earth every eighty-eight minutes. When last in orbit, Major Titov says that he managed to put in a good seven hours, without one bad dream, and without a single sleeping pill.
